<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>Alpas</title>

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Halant:300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html, body {
            background-color: ghostwhite;
            color: #3F3D56;
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            align-items: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex-grow: 1;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .title {
            font-family: 'Halant', sans-serif;
            font-size: 9em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-family: 'Halant', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .text {
            font-family: 'Halant', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .my-md {
            margin: 1em 0;
        }

        .my-lg {
            margin: 3em 0;
        }

        a {
            color: #3F51B5;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title"> 404 </h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle"> Page Not Found </h2>
        <div class="my-lg">
            <img src="/404.svg" alt="Page not found!" width="460px">
        </div>
        <div class="my-md">
            <p class="text">We made a few rounds looking everywhere for that page but we couldn't locate it.</p>
            <p class="text">Getting lost in space is no fun.</p>
            <p class="text"><a href="/">&leftarrow; Let's go home!</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
